Package cea.producer

Class RawRecord

java.lang.Object
cea.producer.RecordDetails
cea.producer.RawRecord
public class RawRecord extends RecordDetails
class that implements a raw record with specified fields needed for real time record simulation based on old records. these two fields and are needed for simulator algorithm for the next simulation, so we keep it with this object which is the simulator method return type.
